Create a complete 2D game using JavaScript and HTML Canvas. The game should be simple and beginner-friendly.

The game type can be one of the following: platformer (like Super Mario Bros.), shooter (like Contra), puzzle (like Tetris), racing (like Hill Climb Racing), or RPG (like Pokemon Red and Blue).

The game must include:

